name: First Visit! Condor (New Livery) 767-330ER [D-ABUA] Landing and Taxi at Calgary Airport ᴴᴰ
description:
Condor's annual seasonal flight to Calgary just started up a few days ago, and already spotters here have been treated to the "hearts for children" livery (which I was unable to catch) and this, their first 767 with the new Thomas Cook Group livery. The video includes the landing and a close up taxi past. ATC is included for the landing portion, with captions! Enjoy the video of this 23 year old 767 looking like new.

Thanks for watching! Please comment, rate, and subscribe!
